      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAX BOSTONIA (7) was a last start winner this course and distance taking a Grade 4/5 in 34.60 in the best time on the card and clocking a personal best as well. Expected to push the clock again. ROMA KEEPING (4) is an honest type rarely out of the money, scoring at this track (34.67) last time and making it three straight wins. Goes very well at the trip finding the frame in each of five starts. Looks suited and expected to run well. VALIDATE (3) jumped favourite and quickly to the front but run down late to finish second (34.86) at this track in a Grade 4/5 over 600m. The form out of his last race has been franked. Expected to feature again. GOLDSTAR SANDLER (2) cannot be underestimated.",
